{"TopicId":31014,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"[Showcase] Post your seat-based creations","CreatedByName":"Cipher29","CreatedById":41440,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-02T22:27:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cipher29","CreatedById":41440,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-02T22:27:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo the first thing we all did in 0.20 was strap Jeb to an SRB, but what else have you done using the seats?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere\u0027s my creation, the Vertically Launched Exploration Vehicle (VLEV):\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/LgxcteJ.jpg?1\u0022 alt=\u0022LgxcteJ.jpg?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/uvnGFwE.jpg?1\u0022 alt=\u0022uvnGFwE.jpg?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECapable of being piggy-backed for easy relocation:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/k9150Nm.jpg?1\u0022 alt=\u0022k9150Nm.jpg?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEnough about me, let\u0027s see what you guys have made!\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-06-02T23:00:50Z\u0022 title=\u002206/02/2013 11:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EJune 2, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Cipher29\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Neotician","CreatedById":68796,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T00:52:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWell, my first idea was to fulfil a life long dream of jeb\u0027s.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/O8F4MtWvpBw?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\