003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbol Prime","CreatedById":57626,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T03:42:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere it is. A never released craft of the BluPlanet Association due to strangely poor reviews during testing. I present you...the Kerbal Toaster. Because we all know there are cannibals out there who would love to get their hands on some kerbal flesh...(you know who you are) \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/j2XsOJi.png\u0022 alt=\u0022j2XsOJi.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/KBZJkgC.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KBZJkgC.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/QKqB1n5.png\u0022 alt=\u0022QKqB1n5.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/BtQZsVu.png\u0022 alt=\u0022BtQZsVu.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI may have overcooked him...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"astropapi1","CreatedById":57507,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T03:55:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sapphire\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Sapphire\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI love reentry,\u003Cp\u003EI love the purple skies,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love big rockets,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love when Kerbals fly,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love the whole game,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd all its sights and sounds,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBoom-de-yah-da, boom-de-yah-da\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBoom-de-yah-da, boom-de-yah-da\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love Laythe\u0027s oceans,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love crash debris,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love to go fast,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love tremendous gees,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI love the whole game,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd all its explosions,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBoom-de-yah-da, boom-de-yah-da\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBoom-de-yah-da, boom-de-yah-da\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDiscovery channel\u0027s song! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGod I miss it. It was the coolest thing ever because they were all singing together! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AntiVi","CreatedById":60038,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T04:05:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Supernovy\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Supernovy\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHere\u0027s a couple of things I\u0027ve made recently:\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/KiozulT\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/KiozulTl.png\u0022 alt=\u0022KiozulTl.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDoes that actually work? without cheating?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ve tried and it didn\u0027t o.O\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sapphire","CreatedById":67918,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T04:09:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAsteroids can be found right here! \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/showthread.php/33713-20-Asteroids-%21%21%21%21\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/showthread.php/33713-20-Asteroids-%21%21%21%21\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBut anyhoo, back to the creations. We\u0027ve strapped a Kerbal to an SRB, correct? Well, how about 48?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd yes, this took awhile to set this up.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/mj94xxO.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022mj94xxO.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe horrific aftermath. D:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/1WNYflH.png\u0022 alt=\u00221WNYflH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"taniwha","CreatedById":57176,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T04:22:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJebadiah having a blast:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://taniwha.org/~bill/ksp-seat/screenshot73.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://taniwha.org/~bill/ksp-seat/screenshot73.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot73.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://taniwha.org/~bill/ksp-seat/screenshot74.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://taniwha.org/~bill/ksp-seat/screenshot74.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot74.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://taniwha.org/~bill/ksp-seat/RCS%20Chair.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ECraft file\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vade","CreatedById":48853,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T04:56:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Supernovy\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Supernovy\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHere\u0027s a couple of things I\u0027ve made recently:\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/2yT09V7\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/2yT09V7l.png\u0022 alt=\u00222yT09V7l.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/KiozulT\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/KiozulTl.png\u0022 alt=\u0022KiozulTl.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAny way you can post the craft file for the pod racer?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Supernovy","CreatedById":29617,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T05:31:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe craft in that picture is long gone, but I\u0027m working on a new one\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/hoDeB13\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/hoDeB13l.png\u0022 alt=\u0022hoDeB13l.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt may take a while though...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mekan1k","CreatedById":48750,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-04T05:41:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/DMg7NhM.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022DMg7NhM.jpg\u0022\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mazlem","CreatedById":57206,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-04T11:45:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFrom the Sepratron challenge:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i222.photobucket.com/albums/dd235/Mazlem/KSP/Sepratron-Challenge2.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Sepratron-Challenge2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fendleton","CreatedById":22867,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-05T08:03:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI give you....the Emergency Orbital Return Vehicle!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/4915761/screenshot1.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot1.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt has no control torque, no docking ability, no SAS/ASAS, no instruments, and uses its RCS unit for \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003Espinning out of\u003C/span\u003E control and de-orbiting.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELet\u0027s try it out.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/4915761/KSP0.2/screenshot2.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/4915761/KSP0.2/screenshot4.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot4.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/4915761/KSP0.2/screenshot6.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot6.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEnd result: Success! Buuuut......Design scrapped because I had better things than this in service already. Plus this thing is nearly impossible to control.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso, to anyone else who wants to make an ejector-seat, I advise the use of the drogue chute, because anything larger will catapult the kerbal out of the chair when it opens unless you have some other means of slowing down beforehand. I do wish we had the ability to start a new ship with a seat *with a kerbal in it* so I don\u0027t have to ruin my \u003Cem\u003Ebeautiful\u003C/em\u003E flying machines with spare Mk.1 pods.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flixxbeatz","CreatedById":29991,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-05T08:09:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/EUVtz7EFU_4?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sapphire","CreatedById":67918,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-05T11:06:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDoes anyone else have a problem with the seats; when switching to a ground-based vehicle that has Kerbals in the seats, they \u0022fall through\u0022 the vehicle and land on the ground, then follow the vehicle around as you try to drive it, and you can\u0027t activate them or remove them from the seats or put them back in, and it\u0027s stuck like that forever?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"veio","CreatedById":71951,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-22T23:16:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI kinda feel bad for my Kerbal in his circle of death but.... it was fun \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/5j3pa22qxombrlt/image.png\u0022 alt=\u0022image.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/mKNtfNjGGoA?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/5ae0lovuhayn939/Catepult%20to%20the%20sea.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ECraft file\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}